  "detailed_description": "Welcome to VERY HARD GAME!!!<br><br>You play as this little blob called Blobby!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2708940/extras/127659330f3e4f24465b06254064a41d.apng?t=1753556890\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2708940/extras/127659330f3e4f24465b06254064a41d.poster.avif?t=1753556890\" class=\"bb_img\" width=64 height=64 /></picture></span><br>Blobby must make it through GameMastrs 100 rooms to win!!!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> You can change Blobby's Color! </li><li> Hard Mode! </li><li> Blind Mode! </li><li> You can Walk! </li><li> You can Die! </li><li> Multiple Endings! </li><li> You might be able to Win!</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Gameplay</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2708940/extras/6d5d5757e622225346fe258ab827692b.poster.avif?t=1753556890\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2708940/extras/6d5d5757e622225346fe258ab827692b.webm?t=1753556890\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2708940/extras/6d5d5757e622225346fe258ab827692b.mp4?t=1753556890\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Don't Touch Walls!</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2708940/extras/035990c4e97ce2c1a00da2634fe99394.poster.avif?t=1753556890\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2708940/extras/035990c4e97ce2c1a00da2634fe99394.webm?t=1753556890\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steams